<section class="gecko-reviews gecko-reviews--embed section-padding" id="customer-reviews">
  <div class="gecko-reviews__wrap page-width">
    <h2 class="gecko-reviews__title">Customer Reviews</h2>

    <div class="gecko-reviews__summary">
      <div class="gecko-reviews__avg">
        <div class="gecko-stars gecko-stars--lg" style="--p: 97.8%;" role="img" aria-label="4.89 / 5"></div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__avg-num">4.89 out of 5</div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__total">Based on 5066 reviews</div>
      </div>

      <div class="gecko-reviews__bars">
        <div class="gecko-reviews__bar-row">
          <span class="gecko-reviews__bar-label">5 <span class="gecko-stars gecko-stars--xs" style="--p:100%;" aria-hidden="true"></span></span>
          <div class="gecko-reviews__bar-track"><div class="gecko-reviews__bar-fill" style="width: 91%;"></div></div>
          <span class="gecko-reviews__bar-count">4619</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__bar-row">
          <span class="gecko-reviews__bar-label">4 <span class="gecko-stars gecko-stars--xs" style="--p:100%;" aria-hidden="true"></span></span>
          <div class="gecko-reviews__bar-track"><div class="gecko-reviews__bar-fill" style="width: 7%;"></div></div>
          <span class="gecko-reviews__bar-count">357</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__bar-row">
          <span class="gecko-reviews__bar-label">3 <span class="gecko-stars gecko-stars--xs" style="--p:100%;" aria-hidden="true"></span></span>
          <div class="gecko-reviews__bar-track"><div class="gecko-reviews__bar-fill" style="width: 2%;"></div></div>
          <span class="gecko-reviews__bar-count">83</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__bar-row">
          <span class="gecko-reviews__bar-label">2 <span class="gecko-stars gecko-stars--xs" style="--p:100%;" aria-hidden="true"></span></span>
          <div class="gecko-reviews__bar-track"><div class="gecko-reviews__bar-fill" style="width: 0%;"></div></div>
          <span class="gecko-reviews__bar-count">4</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__bar-row">
          <span class="gecko-reviews__bar-label">1 <span class="gecko-stars gecko-stars--xs" style="--p:100%;" aria-hidden="true"></span></span>
          <div class="gecko-reviews__bar-track"><div class="gecko-reviews__bar-fill" style="width: 0%;"></div></div>
          <span class="gecko-reviews__bar-count">3</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="gecko-reviews__write">
        <a class="gecko-reviews__write-btn" href="#">Write a review</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="gecko-reviews__filter">
      <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__filter-btn" aria-expanded="false">Pictures First ▾</button>
    </div>

    <div class="gecko-reviews__list" data-gecko-reviews-list data-per-page="3">
      <article class="gecko-reviews__item" data-review-item>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__item-head">
          <div class="gecko-stars" style="--p: 100%;" role="img" aria-label="5 / 5"></div>
          <time class="gecko-reviews__date">06/18/2026</time>
        </div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__author-row">
          <span class="gecko-reviews__author">Genevieve Dew</span>
          <span class="gecko-reviews__verified">Verified</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="gecko-reviews__item-title">The shirt is of good quality</h3>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__item-text rte">
          <p>The shirt I ordered for my hubby came out almost perfect. The color etc. the picture brought tears to his eyes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__votes">
          <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__vote" aria-label="Helpful">👍 <span>8</span></button>
          <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__vote" aria-label="Not helpful">👎 <span>0</span></button>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="gecko-reviews__item" data-review-item>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__item-head">
          <div class="gecko-stars" style="--p: 100%;" role="img" aria-label="5 / 5"></div>
          <time class="gecko-reviews__date">06/15/2026</time>
        </div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__author-row">
          <span class="gecko-reviews__author">Customer Lucy</span>
          <span class="gecko-reviews__verified">Verified</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="gecko-reviews__item-title">50th Birthday Celebration Shirt</h3>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__item-text rte">
          <p>This shirt was a hit for my Fiancé! It was epic. Thank you!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__votes">
          <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__vote" aria-label="Helpful">👍 <span>12</span></button>
          <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__vote" aria-label="Not helpful">👎 <span>0</span></button>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="gecko-reviews__item" data-review-item>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__item-head">
          <div class="gecko-stars" style="--p: 100%;" role="img" aria-label="5 / 5"></div>
          <time class="gecko-reviews__date">06/10/2026</time>
        </div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__author-row">
          <span class="gecko-reviews__author">Kathleen</span>
          <span class="gecko-reviews__verified">Verified</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="gecko-reviews__item-title">Mens Hawaiian shirt</h3>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__item-text rte">
          <p>The shirt is nice quality and our 2 dogs photos are clear. I highly recommend.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gecko-reviews__votes">
          <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__vote" aria-label="Helpful">👍 <span>5</span></button>
          <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__vote" aria-label="Not helpful">👎 <span>0</span></button>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <nav class="gecko-reviews__pagination" data-gecko-reviews-pagination aria-label="Pagination avis">
      <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__page is-active" data-page="1">1</button>
      <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__page" data-page="2">2</button>
      <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__page" data-page="3">3</button>
      <button type="button" class="gecko-reviews__page gecko-reviews__page--next" data-page="next" aria-label="Suivant">›</button>
    </nav>
  </div>
</section>

<script src="{{ 'gecko-reviews.js' | asset_url }}" defer="defer"></script>
